      "acceptanceCriteria": "Order-of-accuracy tests and method of manufactured solutions must confirm solver convergence behavior for rotating-frame hemolysis transport at MRL 5.",
      "rationale": "Order-of-accuracy studies were performed for the baseline flow solver but not extended to the hemolysis scalar transport equation. Achieved level 2 is insufficient for MRL 5 requirements."
