      "achievedLevel": 3,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "The hemolysis index QoI used in validation must be demonstrably the same metric as the clinical acceptance threshold; mapping from NIH to modified power-law index must be documented.",
      "rationale": "The NIH hemolysis index used in bench validation differs from the modified power-law index used in the CFD model; a formal mapping with uncertainty characterization is absent. Achieved level 3 falls short of required level 4."
