      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Validation activities must be conducted on the same pump geometry and operating envelope as the COU; surrogate geometry use must be justified with similarity analysis.",
      "rationale": "Validation was conducted on the FDA generic pump geometry, which differs from the clinical VAD device in impeller tip clearance and volute design. No formal similarity analysis was provided to support extrapolation. Achieved level 2 is well below required level 5."
