      "acceptanceCriteria": "Turbulence model and hemolysis constitutive model form uncertainty must be quantified; alternative model forms must be evaluated to bound model-form error contribution to total prediction uncertainty.",
      "rationale": "Model form uncertainty for both the SST k-omega turbulence closure and the Giersiepen-Wurzinger hemolysis power-law exponents was not evaluated. No alternative model forms were tested. This is a critical epistemic gap at MRL 5."
