    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The credibility assessment package for COU2 VAD hemolysis prediction has been reviewed and accepted for submission under the Minimal profile. All 13 credibility factors have been evaluated or flagged as epistemic gaps with documented rationale. Seven factors were formally assessed; six were identified as not assessed at MRL 5. The package hash confirms content integrity at time of submission. The decision outcome reflects acceptance of the assessment package itself as a complete and internally consistent credibility evidence record, not acceptance of the model for regulatory use — the model decision remains Not Accepted pending resolution of credibility factor gaps.",
